{"title":"历史，没有晚点——为香港回归而歌","authors":["雷抒雁"],"dates":[{"year":1997,"month":6,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史，没有晚点"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——为香港回归而歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷抒雁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，整个世界"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都把目光转向东方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看一颗璀璨的明珠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被摘下占领者的王冠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国，郑重地把它收回"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻轻地轻轻地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缀在自己的胸前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是百年乐章中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最华彩的乐段"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是拥有十二亿人口的国度"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最盛大的庆典"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史，没有晚点"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有怜悯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"占领者一丝一毫的贪婪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那曾经用贫穷和苦难"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写就的史页"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被中国用大手轻轻翻过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面对百年的耻辱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国大声说：再见"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一百年的时间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"严实如一块钢板"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了你，香港"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们一寸一寸把它剪断"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"剪断年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"剪断月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"剪断三万多个"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难熬的白天和夜晚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那些陈旧的时间的落叶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已经堆满了所有的博物馆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一页上都写着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"屈辱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"期盼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和尊严……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终于剪碎百年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１９９７年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"７月１日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"零点"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个民族为自己的尊严而狂欢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们把大街小巷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用清水洗上千遍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"占领者的马蹄曾把这里污染"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们把旗杆擦上万遍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五星红旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将从这里升上香港的蓝天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩灯的瀑布"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从高楼喷向每一间铺面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜花的河流"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从高山流向每一座庭院"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锣呵，鼓呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敲响的是民族的自豪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狮呵，龙呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舞动的是百年的心愿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"酒杯里，盛满百年的祝福"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝天上，洒满彩色的语言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今夜，在这山边海边"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烧一道纸祭奠我们的祖先"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让无数不散的亡灵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从此永远闭合双眼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从林则徐到邓大人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请你们并肩站在太平山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民族英雄的雕像"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才是这座名城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真正的灵魂和肝胆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让钟声告诉未来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史，永远记住这一天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"断指的伤痛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抽搐了一百年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁会忘记"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被劫掠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被割裂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被羞辱折磨的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那些时间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁的手能抚平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"先烈们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"目光里燃烧的火焰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"香港啊，今天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要用这层层海浪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把你的周身吻遍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吻你被列强利舰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"割成的累累伤痕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吻你被叫成洋人名字的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一道海湾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百年来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是万里长城砖石上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被炮火轰开的一片塌陷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是漫漫海疆锚链上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被刺刀砍落的一节链环"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是我们民族胸前不肯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愈合的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个流血的弹眼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾经流出的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是白银和血汗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流进的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却是鸦片和强权"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，我们终于能将手臂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舒展"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南海北海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东海黄海渤海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一朵浪花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赠你一句祝福"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条浪涌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送你一串花环"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一百年的等待"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是柔情蜜意的相约"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炮舰下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不会有公正和允诺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百年等待"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是为了寻找"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你不是酒后迷路的醉汉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"香港"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你不是走失的孩子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也不是不慎被盗的金碗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"香港，我们不曾把你遗失"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你就在我们身边"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"睁眼，闭眼，看得见"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"近在咫尺梦难圆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一百年的等待"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是绿草和春天相约"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以回黄转绿面对挫折"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一百年的等待"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是榕树和大地相约"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以千条根的坚定和信念扭结"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当牺牲者的血液"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亮成红旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当倒下的英灵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"复活成战士站立"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史，选择了四川乡音发言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幽默平和"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却无比坚定"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一如打入岩石里的钢钎"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他以智慧的钥匙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打开沉沉的锈锁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史以轻快的脚步"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨过艰难的门坎"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给中国，留下一条康庄大道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给香港，留下一个繁荣的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给世界，留下一个不朽的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"典范"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当伟大的庆典就要拉开序幕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟人啊，您却离开我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留下一个世纪的遗憾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给１９９７年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寒冷的春天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们曾经和１９９７相约"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"７月１日，零点敲过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即使抬着您的轮椅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也要您去看看香港"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看看洗雪百年耻辱之后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海风吹得多么清新"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紫荆花开得多么鲜艳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们曾经和１９９７相约"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不管是在秋季，还是冬天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即使搀扶您的双臂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也要您登上太平山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看看香港的层楼海湾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么自豪的气魄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么灿烂的明天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到自己的土地上去走一走"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了这一个伟大的心愿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小平同志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整个民族都曾经为您祝福"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整个香港都曾经把您期盼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相信您强有力的手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"定会把握生命的风帆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，等您啊，小平同志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五星红旗，等您亲手升起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"团圆的酒，等您举杯同干"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等您，浅水湾望穿秋水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等您，太平山望断云天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热爱大海的人啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天维多利亚多情的海湾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已是我们自己的海面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪花雪白"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海水碧蓝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自由的鸥鸟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"展翅在我们自己的蓝天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到这里来游泳吧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让丝绸般的海水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻轻地滑过您的指尖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今夜，整个中国都能听见"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听见您的心声如潮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拍打着港城美丽的海岸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听见您脚步如风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在自己的土地上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走得自由而又悠闲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看那簇簇紫荆花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不正是您的笑容"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依然明亮乐观"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七月的风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"该是您的呼吸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"急促而又温暖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，祖国团圆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史，没有晚点"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无数次抚摸你曲曲折折的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地图"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无数次隔岸相望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"香港今天，我们手拉手，肩并肩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我们一起细说"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"关于奋斗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"关于繁荣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"关于明天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新世纪的曙光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已照彻中国的窗口"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们出发"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正鼓荡我们的船帆……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（作者单位：鲁迅文学院）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":11,"page_end":11}